sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler
    participant Indexer as kvcache.Indexer<br/>(Go Library)
    participant TokenPool as tokenization.Pool
    participant UdsTokenizer as UDS Tokenizer Service<br/>UDS gRPC / 8082 Health
    participant TokenProc as kvblock.TokenProcessor<br/>(FNV-64a)
    participant Index as kvblock.Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant Scorer as kvblock.Scorer
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZmqSub as zmqSubscriber<br/>(ZMQ SUB)
    participant Pool as kvevents.Pool<br/>(Sharded Workers)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Reconciler as Pod Reconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)

    Note over Scheduler, Scorer: Flow 1: KV-Cache-Aware Scoring (Read Path)

    Scheduler->>Indexer: GetPodScores(prompt, model, pods)<br/>Go API call
    Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize(prompt, model)
    TokenPool->>UdsTokenizer: gRPC Tokenize over UDS<br/>/tmp/tokenizer/tokenizer-uds.socket<br/>plaintext
    UdsTokenizer-->>TokenPool: TokenizeResponse(input_ids[])
    TokenPool-->>Indexer: Token IDs
    Indexer->>TokenProc: GenerateBlockKeys(tokens, blockSize)<br/>FNV-64a chained hashing
    TokenProc-->>Indexer: Block hash keys[]
    Indexer->>Index: Lookup(keys[])<br/>In-memory or Redis/6379
    Index-->>Indexer: map[key] → pod locations
    Indexer->>Scorer: Score(podHits, strategy)<br/>Longest prefix match + device weighting
    Scorer-->>Indexer: map[pod] → float64 scores
    Indexer-->>Scheduler: GetPodScoresResponse(PodScore[])

    Note over vLLM, Index: Flow 2: KV-Cache Event Ingestion (Write Path)

    vLLM->>ZmqSub: KV-cache event<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>msgpack encoded, plaintext
    ZmqSub->>Pool: Forward event<br/>Go channel (FNV-1a pod affinity)
    Pool->>Pool: Decode msgpack<br/>BlockStored/BlockRemoved/AllBlocksCleared
    Pool->>Index: Store/Remove block<br/>In-memory or Redis/6379

    Note over Reconciler, ZmqSub: Flow 3: Pod Auto-Discovery

    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Watch pods (label selector)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Reconciler: Pod Added/Deleted events
    Reconciler->>ZmqSub: Create/Remove ZMQ subscriber<br/>Connect to pod:5557/TCP
